'''Kurth''' was the leader of [[Ship Kurth]] and one of the five [[High Captains (Luskan)|High Captains]] of the city of [[Luskan]] in [[1367 DR]]. Due to the traditions of the High Captains, his real name was rarely used but it is highly likely that he is not the first High Captain Kurth. Along with his peers he was an experienced adventurer and a former pirate.
